The input parameter "row" must be a positive integer representing the number of rows in the grid.
The input parameter "col" must be a positive integer representing the number of columns in the grid.
The input parameter "cells" must be a 2D array of integers representing the grid, where each element represents a cell and its value can be either 0 (land) or 1 (water).
The grid must have at least one row and one column.
The grid must have at least one land cell.
